description: TrashDay uses the TDS calendar (example here: http://www.texasdisposal.com/sites/default/files/uploads/TDS_ResidentialServiceCalendar-2016.pdf) to figure out when your next trash or recycle day is.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next trash day
Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next recycle pickup
Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next trash pickup
name: Apache Trash Day
shortDescription: Tells you when the next trash and/or recycle day is in the neighborhood
